6 b. An administrator of a Licensing Board.
7 3. Any delegate may be removed or suspended from office as provided by the
8 laws of the State from which the delegate is appointed.
9 4. The Participating State Licensing Board shall fill any vacancy occurring in
10 the Commission within sixty days.
11 5. Each delegate shall be entitled to one vote on all matters voted on by the
