14 by such other means as provided in the bylaws. The bylaws may provide
15 for delegates’ participation in meetings by telecommunications, video
16 conference, or other means of communication.
17 6. The Commission shall meet at least once during each calendar year.
18 Additional meetings shall be held as set forth in this Compact and the
19 bylaws.
20 7. The Commission shall establish by Rule a term of office for delegates.
