32 whom the claim is made had a reasonable basis for believing occurred within
33 the scope of Commission employment, duties or responsibilities; provided
34 that nothing in this paragraph shall be construed to protect any such person
35 from suit or liability for any damage, loss, injury, or liability caused by the
